package.description:
**To play on other clusters, you need to have an account on each one**

Features of fashion:
Simple selection of servers in other clusters;
There is no need for permanent copying / deleting of files;
Do not need constant updates when you exit the "micro patches";
All established fashion will be available;
Easy installation;

Mod is able to collect and display the following statistics in the system channel:
&#92;tCredit statistics;
&#92;tStatistics of experience;
&#92;tDamage statistics;
&#92;tStatistics expenses;
&#92;tStatistics bonuses from reserves;
&#92;tStatistics penalties;
&#92;ttime statistics;
&#92;tStatistics combat effectiveness;
&#92;tRatings combat effectiveness (WGR, EFF, BS, WN6, WN7, WN8, WN8KTTC, BR);
&#92;tDetailed statistics of the last battle;
&#92;tStatistics Account at the beginning of the session;
&#92;tThe impact of the current session on the account;

Author: Mick42 and Andre_V; 
This mod changes the standard voice acting crew sounds (screams, laughter, singing, dancing with a tambourine, etc.) minions film “Despicable Me” and “Despicable Me 2”. 

